OL,3,C'Enough is enough' says O'Neill on
OL,4,Cviolence against women
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland's First Minister has
OL,7,Fissued a rallying call to the
OL,8,Fcommunity in the wake of the Natalie
OL,9,FMcNally murder trail and following the
OL,10,Fdeaths of two women in recent weeks
OL,11,Fsaying "enough is enough".
OL,13,FMichelle O'Neill was speaking in the
OL,14,FGreat Hall at Parliament Buildings in
OL,15,FBelfast following the murder of Amy
OL,16,FDoherty in Londonderry and Ellie
OL,17,FFlanagan in Fermanagh this month.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
