OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774451488
OL,3,C'Enough is enough' says O'Neill on
OL,4,Cviolence against women
OL,6,FShe acknowledged there was a "huge
OL,7,Fproblem" in Northern Ireland with
OL,8,Fviolence against women and girls but
OL,9,Fsaid it was "fixable" with the help of
OL,10,Fall in society.
OL,12,FMs O'Neill took the press conference
OL,13,Falone. Asked about the absence of the
OL,14,Fdeputy First Minister Emma Little-
OL,15,FPengelly, she said there was "no
OL,16,Fissue" saying diary events had
OL,17,Fprevented a dual press conference in
OL,18,FStormont and the two would be at an
OL,19,Fevent later.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
