OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774451488
OL,3,C'Enough is enough' says O'Neill on
OL,4,Cviolence against women
OL,6,FThe Sinn Fein MLA added: "This is
OL,7,Fabout me coming out to offer my
OL,8,Fcondolence to the McNally family and
OL,9,Foffer my love and support to them."
OL,11,FLater in a separate press conference,
OL,12,FMs Little-Pengelly said: "The level of
OL,13,Fviolence against women and girls in
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland is completely
OL,15,Funacceptable.
OL,17,FShe added: "Our strategy is about
OL,18,Fprevention, it is about that longer
OL,19,Fterm, it is about getting into
OL,20,Fschools, getting into sports clubs,
OL,21,Fgetting into youth clubs."
OL,26,@nD@Kqr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
