OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774451488
OL,3,C'Enough is enough' says O'Neill on
OL,4,Cviolence against women
OL,6,FMs McNally was 15 weeks pregnant when
OL,7,Fshe was beaten and stabbed at her home
OL,8,Fin Lurgan on December 18 2022.
OL,10,FMs O'Neill said: "Once again we find
OL,11,Fourselves talking about more women
OL,12,Fbeing killed, more women being subject
OL,13,Fto violence and this is a problem that
OL,14,Fwe have across our society," she told
OL,15,Freporters.
OL,17,F"We have a job ` all of us
OL,18,Fcollectively as a society ` in terms
OL,19,Fof ending violence against women and
OL,20,Fgirls.
OL,26,@rD@ROUvD@\O]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
