PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774451488
OL,3,C'Enough is enough' says O'Neill on
OL,4,Cviolence against women
OL,6,F"Enough is enough.
OL,8,F"It needs to be an ongoing
OL,9,Fconversation, we need to challenge the
OL,10,Fmisogyny we see every day, we need all
OL,11,Fof us to work together to collectively
OL,12,Fturn the misogynistic element we have
OL,13,Fout there in our society.
OL,15,F"We have a huge problem. It is a
OL,16,Ffixable problem but it is going to
OL,17,Frequire all of us working together."
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
