OL,3,C'Enough is enough' says O'Neill on
OL,4,Cviolence against women
OL,6,FMs O'Neill also commended Ms McNally's
OL,7,Ffamily for "using the most harrowing
OL,8,Fexperience of their life" to raise
OL,9,Fawareness around violence against
OL,10,Fwomen and girls.
OL,12,F"They never gave up in the fight for
OL,13,Fjustice for Natalie and I hope that
OL,14,Fyesterday's verdict gives them some
OL,15,Fcomfort in terms of there being an
OL,16,Foutcome to the case, however none of
OL,17,Fthat brings their beautiful Natalie
OL,18,Fback," she added.
OL,26,@oD@LOUpD@YO]tD@AOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
