OL,3,C'Enough is enough' says O'Neill on
OL,4,Cviolence against women
OL,6,FLater at a joint press conference,
OL,7,Fboth Michelle O'Neill and Emma Little-
OL,8,FPengelly spoke to UTV and reiterated
OL,9,Fthat they are both committed to
OL,10,Ftackling violence against women as
OL,11,Fwell as their support of the verdict
OL,12,Fin the Natalie McNally murder trial.
